fl
Time Complexity
O(N × M)
Reason
N = Number of strings
M = Length of the first string

For every character, we compare it with all strings.

Space Complexity
O(1)
Reason

No extra data structure is used.

Important Points
Use the first string as reference.
Compare characters index by index.
Stop immediately when mismatch occurs.
If one string ends before others, return prefix till that point.
If no common prefix exists, return "".
Empty string can make the answer empty.
